'''维格纳效应'''<ref>{{cite book |editor=王运 |title=新编英汉科技大词典 |date=1988 |publisher=[[科学技术文献出版社|科学技术文献出版社]] |isbn=978-7-5023-0064-7 |url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/%E6%96%B0%E7%BC%96%E8%8B%B1%E6%B1%89%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%AF%8D%E5%85%B8/dji5AAAAIAAJ?hl=en&gbpv=1&bsq=%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%B4%E6%A0%BC%E7%BA%B3%E6%95%88%E5%BA%94%E2%80%9D&kptab=overview |accessdate=2021-04-14 |language=zh}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Wigner effect}}，名自[[尤金·维格纳|尤金·维格纳]]<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1063/1.1707653 | title = Theoretical Physics in the Metallurgical Laboratory of Chicago | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-applied-physics_1946-11_17_11/page/857 | year = 1946 | last1 = Wigner | first1 = E. P. | journal = [[Journal_of_Applied_Physics|Journal of Applied Physics]] | volume = 17 | issue = 11 | pages = 857–863|bibcode = 1946JAP....17..857W }}</ref>），也作'''击离效应'''<ref>{{cite web |title=discomposition effect - 擊離效應 |url=https://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/526367/ |website=terms.naer.edu.tw |publisher=[[国家教育研究院|国家教育研究院]] |accessdate=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414204710/https://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/526367/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang|en|discomposition effect}}），指的是原子在经受[[中子辐射|中子辐射]]的时候会产生位移的现象。对于[[石墨|石墨]]晶体而言，以[[快中子|快中子]]为主导的维格纳效应会导致材料的晶体结构变形。<ref>{{cite web |title=Wigner effect |url=https://www.euronuclear.org/glossary/wigner-effect/ |website=ENS |accessdate=2021-04-14 |date=2019-08-15 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415201647/https://www.euronuclear.org/glossary/wigner-effect/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1943年，美国化学家米尔顿·伯顿（{{lang|en|Milton Burton}}）和T·J·纽伯特（{{lang|en|T.J. Neubert}}）发现该效应。<ref>{{cite web |title=Radiation - Neutrons |url=https://www.britannica.com/science/radiation/Neutrons#ref398881 |website=[[Encyclopedia_Britannica|Encyclopedia Britannica]] |accessdate=2021-04-14 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416223647/https://www.britannica.com/science/radiation/Neutrons#ref398881 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

